        public void deactivate(java.net.URI userId,

        Deactivates secret keys for the specified user.

        API Call: POST /object/user-secret-keys/{uid}/deactivate

        Parameters:
        userId - User identifier.
        param - Parameters to deactivate the secret keys. If no keys are specified, will delete all keys.
